						<summary>

						<p>This inscription refers to a gift of land situated in Chōḻapāṇḍyavaḷanāḍu, as Tirunāmattukkāṇi to the temple at Tirukōlakkuḍi in Puramalaināḍu by a native of Kāraiyūr in Kēraḷasiṅga-vaḷanāḍu.</p>						

